en鈥檛 any by the vanities. You had to wash your hands in one room, then run dripping to another to dry them in the bathroom 鈥?which didn鈥檛 have enough towel rails anyway... not very 4*.I had to take things out of the advertised fridge in order to put anything in it. But if you鈥檙e looking for a well-stocked mini bar, the Wyndham鈥檚 your hotel!Would we stay at the Boston Wyndham again? Most definitely. In a heartbeat. 
